-total spending refers to the sum of the grand totals of all transactions made by a customer; 
-the highest total spending implies that the list is ordered in descending order based on the total spending; 
-the categories mentioned refer to the ones that the customers have made purchases in.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT category_id 
FROM transactions 
ORDER BY category_id ASC;

